{"lemma":"رَجْمُ","slug":"رَجْمُ","root":"ر.ج.م","root_slug":"ر-ج-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ج-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَجْم","root":"رجم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14968","n14974","n14975","n14976"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stone, to lapidate, to throw stones at"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hurl insults at","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cuss, to rail"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to expel, repudiate, banish, oust, exile, drive away"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَجَمَ (rajama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stoning, lapidation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"meteorite","examples":[{"text":"وَلَقَدۡ زَيَّنَّا ٱلسَّمَآءَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا بِمَصَٰبِيحَ وَجَعَلۡنَٰهَا رُجُومٗا لِّلشَّيَٰطِينِۖ وَأَعۡتَدۡنَا لَهُمۡ عَذَابَ ٱلسَّعِيرِ.","english":"And verily We have beautified the world's heaven with lamps, and We have made them shooting stars for the devils, and for them We have prepared the doom of flame."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"missile, projectile"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sentence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conjecture"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grave, tumulus"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Aramaic רגם (ragam), Classical Syriac ܪܓܡ (rəḡam) and Hebrew רָגַם (ragám)."},"ipa":["/ra.d͡ʒa.ma/","/rad͡ʒm/","/ra.d͡ʒam/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14968","headword_ar":"رَجْمٌ","root":"rjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throwing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"casting, of stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) this is its primary meaning: (S, TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamahu","text_ar":"رَجَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast, stones at him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pelted him with stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he struck him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smote him, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajam","text_ar":"رَجَم"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujuwmN","text_ar":"رُجُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as an inf. n.: thus some explain the saying, in the Kur [lxvii. 5],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajoEalonaAhaA rujuwmFA lil$~ayaATiyni","text_ar":"وَجْعَلْنَاهَا رُجُومًا لِلشَّيَاطِينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And we have made them for casting at the devils;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning shooting stars, which are believed to be hurled at the devils that listen by stealth, beneath the lowest heaven, to the words of the angels therein: but see other explanations below, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (S, TA,) The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slaying"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stoning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"putting to death by stoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) So in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomu Alv~ay~ibayoni A_i*aA zanayaA","text_ar":"رَجْمُ الثَّيِّبَيْنِ اـِذَا زَنَيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The slaying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stoning, of the two married persons when they have committed adultery"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [(assumed tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the ground with the feet.] One says of a camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarojumu AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"يَرْجُمُ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"batters, the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"], i. e., with his feet; which implies commendation: (TA:) and so one says of a horse; (K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yurojumu fiY AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"يُرْجُمُ فِى الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a yarojumu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ يَرْجُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came beating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battering, the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passing along with an ardent and a rapid running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K, * TA.) [See also 8.] ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cursing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reviling."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^arojuman~aka","text_ar":"لَاَرْجُمَنَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur xix. 47, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly revile thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, Jel, TA: see also another explanation below, in this paragraph:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly cast stones at thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, Jel,) so that thou shalt die, or shalt remove far from me. (Bd.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamotuhu biAlqawoli","text_ar":"رَجَمْتُهُ بِالقَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I uttered foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil, speech against him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajabahu","text_ar":"رَجَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"driving away; expelling; putting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placing, at a distance, away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cutting off from friendly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loving communion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intercourse; forsaking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abandoning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b8-  Also [as being likened to the throwing of stones, in doing which one is not sure of hitting the mark,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qa*ofN","text_ar":"قَذْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlgayobi","text_ar":"بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  [The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaking of that which is hidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has not become apparent to the speaker;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1048},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjecturing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaking conjecturally:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and (K, TA) some say (TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayobN","text_ar":"غَيْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a doubting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA: [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayobu","text_ar":"العَيْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algayobu","text_ar":"الغَيْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zan~N","text_ar":"ظَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an opining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a conjecturing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajama biAlgayobi","text_ar":"رَجَمَ بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke of that which he did not know."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 494.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajama biAlZ~an~i","text_ar":"رَجَمَ بِالظَّنِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke conjecturally:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he conjectured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opined."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xviii. 21.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAlahu rajomFA","text_ar":"قَالَهُ رَجْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said it conjecturally."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) Hence also, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomFA baAlgayobi","text_ar":"رَجْمًا بَالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xviii. 21], (S, TA,) (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Speaking conjecturally of that which is hidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unknown;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as indicated in the S and TA: or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjecturing in a case hidden"},{"kind":"text","text":"from them. (Jel.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla rajomFA biAlgayobi","text_ar":"قَالَ رَجْمًا بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said conjecturally,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaking of that which was hidden from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unknown by him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without evidence, and without proof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra rajomFA laA yuwqafu EalaY Haqiyqapi A^amorihi","text_ar":"صَارَ رَجْمًا لَا يُوقَفُ عَلَى حَقِيقَةِ اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became a subject of conjecture, the real state of the case whereof one was not to be made to know"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^arojuman~aka","text_ar":"لَاَرْجُمَنَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xix. 47, of which two explanations have been mentioned above], means [accord. to some]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly say of thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[though]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaking of that which is hidden"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from me"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unknown"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by me"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what thou dislikest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hatest."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lisaAnN yurojumu","text_ar":"لِسَانٌ يُرْجُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if the latter word be not a mistranscription for ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirojamN","text_ar":"مِرْجَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tongue that is chaste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perspicuous, and copious, in speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trjm","text_ar":"ترجم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b10-  See also the next paragraph, in three places."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Msb","Bd","Jel","Z","MA"]},{"entry_id":"n14974","headword_ar":"رَجْمٌ","root":"rjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. [of 1, q. v.], used as an appellative, (Bd in lxvii. 5,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is thrown,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast, like as is a stone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujuwmN","text_ar":"رُجُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd ib., and K.) Hence, in the Kur (ubi suprà),"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaEalonaAhaA","text_ar":"وَجَعَلْنَاهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujuwmFA lil$~ayaATiyni","text_ar":"رُجُومًا لِلشَّيَاطِينِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And we have made them things to be cast at the devils;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning shooting stars: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujumo","text_ar":"رُجُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we have made them to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjectures to the devils"},{"kind":"text","text":"of mankind; i. e., to the astrologers. (Bd, TA. [See another explanation in the first sentence of this art.])       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A friend;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a true,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincere, friend;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a special,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"particular, friend;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliylN","text_ar":"خَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cup-companion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compotator."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, K.) See also the last signification in the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14975","headword_ar":"رَجَمٌ","root":"rjm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stones"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are placed upon a grave."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A grave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA;) because stones are collected together upon it; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomapN","text_ar":"رَجْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujomapN","text_ar":"رُجْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamN","text_ar":"رَجَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arjaAmN","text_ar":"اَرجَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi A^arojaAmu EaAdK","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ اَرْجَامُ عَادٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"These are the graves of"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the tribe of] 'Ád: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujomapN","text_ar":"رُجْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujamN","text_ar":"رُجَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijaAmN","text_ar":"رِجَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies also, like as does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujumN","text_ar":"رُجُمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high stones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are set up upon a grave:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or both these signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sign"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is set up upon a grave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tombstone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 2] : (K:) or the former of them ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujomapN","text_ar":"رُجْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones collected together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though they were the graves of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tribe of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"'Ád;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA;) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijaAmN","text_ar":"رِجَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or it is sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujamN","text_ar":"رُجَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijaAmN","text_ar":"رِجَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"which signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large stones, less then"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riDaAm","text_ar":"رِضَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riDaAm","text_ar":"رِضَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes collected together upon a grave to form a gibbous covering to it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b3-  Also (i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamN","text_ar":"رَجَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of oven such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tan~uwr","text_ar":"تَنُّور"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juforapN","text_ar":"جُفْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jym","text_ar":"جيم"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the K, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A round space in the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as in other lexicons,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuforapN","text_ar":"حُفْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity, in the ground, made by digging,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"natural"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brothers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brethren:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a quasipl. n.:] sing., accord. to Kr, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamN","text_ar":"رَجَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [so that the latter is used as a sing. and as a pl.;] but (ISd says, TA) I know not how this is. (K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","K","Lth","S"]},{"entry_id":"n14976","headword_ar":"رُجُمٌ","root":"rjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shooting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stars that are cast"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the devils;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rujuwmN","text_ar":"رُجُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as explained by some, pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajomN","text_ar":"رَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. ―         -b2-  See also the second sentence of the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}